dcterms:description: Convolutional Deep Belief Networks (CDBNs) are generative deep learning models that learn a probability distribution over a set of inputs, utilizing stacked convolutional RBMs with an intermediate non-linear max-pooling layer.
dcterms:title: Convolutional Deep Belief Networks (CDBNs)
